Class Component

The base class for xeokit WebViewer components.

Summary
  • Has logging methods
  • Optionally manages lifecycle of owned Components

Methods

Protected error

  • error(message: string): void
    • Defined in webviewer/src/viewer/Component.ts:120

    Logs an error for this component to the JavaScript console.

    The console message will have this format: [ERROR] [<component type> =<component id>: <message>

    Also fires the message as an "error" event on the WebViewer.

    Parameters

    • message: string

      The error message to log

    Returns void

Protected log

  • log(message: string): void
    • Defined in webviewer/src/viewer/Component.ts:88

    Logs a console debugging message for this component.

    The console message will have this format: [LOG] [<component type> <component id>: <message>

    Also fires the message as a "log" event on the parent WebViewer.

    Parameters

    • message: string

      The message to log

    Returns void
